title: Awakenings & My Music Career
description:
**Trigger Warning: Diet Culture, EDs**
With Tasia out sick, Camo runs the show from their bedroom this week! Camo catches us up on their recent lifestyle change, pulls the curtain back on their music career, and answers some of your questions. You won't want to miss this intimate episode of Unfazed and Unbothered!!
This podcast is sponsored by BetterHelp. Go to BetterHelp.com/unfazed to get 10% off your first month.
Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube
